    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/f956d2caa1a0387d790803fc750af5f7.poster.avif?t=1765662610\" width=800 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/f956d2caa1a0387d790803fc750af5f7.webm?t=1765662610\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/f956d2caa1a0387d790803fc750af5f7.mp4?t=1765662610\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/c51c7a0f0d4994d37e7aa488b171bae3.webp?t=1765662610\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Cyra moves smoothly, tightly, and responsively, giving you full control. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Chain insane maneuvers and feel every move as the world tests your reflexes and timing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/ed98bb6eef6f56d93bd043fc20832c25.webp?t=1765662610\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Explore seven hand-drawn planets, packed with hazards and hostile creatures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">All are difficult yet fair. Do you have what it takes to overcome each domain?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/09930697d2c66d6ca895eaa2a6dbe18b.webp?t=1765662610\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Every planet has its own story, movement mechanics, obstacles, and hidden collectibles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Exploration uncovers each area’s secrets and brings you closer to solving the mystery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1845720/extras/4d42265df7e7b825f15ad20cd273ff07.webp?t=1765662610\" width=800 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Cyra travels across the galaxy in search of answers about her father’s disappearance.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Each corner and character reveals more of the mystery and reshapes Cyra’s understanding of herself.</p>",
